description: This common Yulenka purrs with a rating of 5, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 25, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, 1 for East, Leverage for South, and Nine Lives for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [25 Votes, Common]
